{{#> layouts/base}}
{{#*inline "content"}}
<h1>Password Reset Request</h1>

<p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your Hockey Hub account. If you made this request, please click the button below to create a new password.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <strong>This link will expire in {{expirationHours}} hours</strong> for security reasons. If the link expires, you can request a new password reset from the login page.
</div>

<h2>Didn't Request This?</h2>

<p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password won't be changed unless you click the link above and create a new one.</p>

<p>For security reasons, we recommend that you:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
    <li>Use a strong, unique password for your Hockey Hub account</li>
    <li>Enable two-factor authentication for added security</li>
    <li>Contact us immediately if you notice any suspicious activity</li>
</ul>

<div class="divider"></div>

<h2>Having Trouble?</h2>

<p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;">
    {{resetUrl}}
</div>

<h2>Security Information</h2>

<div style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Request Details:</strong></p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">Time: {{requestTime}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">Location: {{location}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">Device: {{deviceInfo}}</p>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@hockeyhub.com">support@hockeyhub.com</a></li>
    <li>Help Center: <a href="{{helpUrl}}">{{helpUrl}}</a></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 30px;">Stay safe,<br>
<strong>The Hockey Hub Security Team</strong></p>

<div class="alert alert-warning" style="margin-top: 30px;">
    <strong>Security Tip:</strong> Hockey Hub will never ask for your password via email, phone, or any other communication method. Always verify that you're on the official Hockey Hub website before entering your credentials.
</div>
{{/inline}}
{{/layouts/base}}